ivardefs.name: appointmentType
ivardefs.desc: The style of appointment or patient that may be booked in the slot (not service type).

ivardefs.name: comment
ivardefs.desc: Comments on the slot to describe any extended information. Such as custom constraints on the slot.

ivardefs.name: end
ivardefs.desc: Date/Time that the slot is to conclude.

ivardefs.name: overbooked
ivardefs.desc: This slot has already been overbooked, appointments are unlikely to be accepted for this time.

ivardefs.name: schedule
ivardefs.desc: The schedule resource that this slot defines an interval of status information.

ivardefs.name: serviceCategory_
ivardefs.desc: A broad categorization of the service that is to be performed during this appointment.

ivardefs.name: serviceType_
ivardefs.desc: The type of appointments that can be booked into this slot (ideally this would be an identifiable service - which is at a location, rather than the location itself). If provided then this overrides the value provided on the availability resource.

ivardefs.name: specialty_
ivardefs.desc: The specialty of a practitioner that would be required to perform the service requested in this appointment.

ivardefs.name: start
ivardefs.desc: Date/Time that the slot is to begin.

properties.desc: A slot of time on a schedule that may be available for booking appointments.
